OL,5, A Boeing engineer has told US lawmakers
OL,6, that he was harassed and threatened    
OL,7, after he raised concerns about the     
OL,8, safety of the company's planes.        
OL,10,FWhistleblower Sam Salehpour said       
OL,11,FWednesday that his boss berated him in 
OL,12,Fa 40-minute call and his tyre was      
OL,13,Fpunctured by a nail.                   
OL,15,FHis claims will be considered as part  
OL,16,Fof a congressional investigation into  
OL,17,Fsafety at the manufacturing giant.     
OL,19,FBoeing has said it is co-operating with
OL,20,Fthe investigation.                     
